articles.author: @jamewils
articles.description:
My #thread on Rs.2000 notes.   

Total number of Rs. 2000 notes was reduced from
33,632 lakhs on 31/03/2018 to
21,420 lakhs on 31/03/2022,  
ie,36.3% reduction in 5 years!  

But value-wise, it is drastically reduced from 
50.2% of total value in 2017 to 
13.8% of same in 2022
